def main():

            deg[u]+=1; deg[v]+=1

            adj[i] = set(adj[i])

        nodes.sort(key=lambda x: deg[x], reverse=True)
        K = 300
        L = nodes[:K] if n> K else nodes
        dl = [deg[u] for u in L]

                break

                    break

                if v in ui:
                    cur -= 1
                if cur > ans:
                    ans = cur
        print(ans)
